<!--T:4-->
The preferences system of FreeCAD, located under menu {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences}}, is very complex. The '''BIM Setup''' dialog offers a simplified version of it, by gathering the settings most commonly used for BIM work in one simple screen. Changing anything there has the same effect as changing the corresponding setting in the Preferences.

